asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Nordica-FireArrow-80-Pro-Skis-with-N-Pro-2S-Bindings-2013/277165P,default,pd.html  The versatile Nordica FireArrow 80 Pro Skis are for the skier who really only skis for one reason: Fun! They packed with features to ensure every turn is as fun as the last one. It has a full camber design to with contact points for precise turn initiation and edge grip. You will have the confidence to improve with the help of the stability that the full camber offers with speed, rebound and edge grip. The N Pro 2S create more balance and control on each turn. Every twist, every turn and every moment on the mountain going over groomers, pow and trails will be a blast with the help of the Nordica FireArrow 80 Pro Skis.
